					<h1 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">Open letter: Ban surveillance-based advertising</h1>
										<div class="lead-text" itemprop="description">
						<p>This letter has been sent by the undersigned to EU &#038; US regulators, to urge them to take action on banning surveillance-based ads, as recommended by the Norwegian Consumer Council.</p>
